<ARTICLETYPE>Correspondence</ARTICLETYPE>
<RECORDNO>975011872</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
AS someone who likes to take advice from those with no vested interest in
controversial issues may I thank the Meat and Livestock Commission for their
recent advertisement which no doubt has reassured many people about BSE?
John F Robins,
Organising Secretary,
Animal Concern,
62 Old Dumbarton Road,
Glasgow.
</TEXT>
